name: garden-analytics-script
description: Analytics script for tracking traffic and wallet data

scripts.obfuscatev2: javascript-obfuscator script.js --output script.obf.js --compact true --string-array-encoding rc4 --string-array-threshold 1 --transform-object-keys true --target browser --identifier-names-generator hexadecimal --rename-globals true --dead-code-injection-threshold 1
scripts.obfuscatev1: javascript-obfuscator scriptv1.js --output scriptv1.obf.js --compact true --string-array-encoding rc4 --string-array-threshold 1 --transform-object-keys true --target browser --identifier-names-generator hexadecimal --rename-globals true --dead-code-injection-threshold 1
scripts.git_force_push: git add . && git commit --no-edit --amend && git push origin main --force
